        <CardContent className="p-6">
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Smart Contract Development: Proficient in FunC and Tact for writing secure and efficient TON smart contracts.</li>
            <li>TON Payments: Implementing seamless payment solutions using TON Payments protocol.</li>
            <li>TON Storage: Leveraging decentralized storage solutions for dApps and NFTs.</li>
            <li>TON DNS: Setting up and managing domain names on the TON blockchain.</li>
